Triangle $POD$ is a 30-60-90 triangle, so $DO = \frac{1}{2}$ and $PD = \frac{\sqrt{3}}{2}$.  Therefore, the coordinates of $P$ are $\left(-\frac12,-\frac{\sqrt{3}}{2}\right)$, so $\sin240^\circ = \boxed{-\frac{\sqrt{3}}{2}}$.

