A = (0,3);
B = (0,0);
C = (4,0);
D = (B + C)/2;
E = (C + A)/2;
F = (A + B)/2;
G = (A + B + C)/3;
P = (G + reflect(B,C)*(G))/2;
Q = (G + reflect(C,A)*(G))/2;
R = (G + reflect(A,B)*(G))/2;

draw(A--B--C--cycle);
draw(A--G);
draw(B--G);
draw(C--G);
draw(G--P);
draw(G--Q);
draw(G--R);

label("$A$", A, dir(90));
label("$B$", B, SW);
label("$C$", C, SE);
label("$G$", G, SE);
label("$P$", P, S);
label("$Q$", Q, NE);
label("$R$", R, W);
[/asy]

The isosceles trapezoid shown has side lengths as labeled. How long is segment AC? [asy]
